# maturity.ttl ŌĆö Pack Maturity Model as typed individuals.
# GENERATED-DOC SOURCE: docs/packs/PACK_MATURITY_MODEL.md is GENERATED from this
# file by the `docs-pack-maturity-model` rule in ggen.toml. Edit THIS file.
# Score cells were transcribed programmatically (byte-faithful) from the
# 2026-07-18 hand-audited tables, then extended with the ggen-verify-pack row
# (2026-07-19). Each mat:d1..d7 literal carries the cell's level + artifact
